  title="GlowPicked - AI-Powered Reviews for Luxury Beauty & Skincare"
  description="Discover the best luxury beauty and skincare products on Amazon through AI-powered review analysis. Data-driven recommendations based on thousands of real customer reviews."
  keywords="luxury beauty reviews, expensive skincare, Amazon beauty products, AI product reviews, premium cosmetics, high-end skincare"
>
